@startuml
[*] --> Unpaired : New Employee Created

Unpaired --> PairingInitiated : Admin generates Pair QR
PairingInitiated --> Paired : Employee scans QR & registers device
PairingInitiated --> Unpaired : Token expires (5 min)

Paired --> Active : Employee checks in
Active --> Paired : Employee checks out

Paired --> Unpaired : Admin unpairs device
Active --> Unpaired : Admin unpairs device

Unpaired --> [*] : Employee deleted
@enduml
